data.text:
So what character/celebrity did I find starts to like the both of them? (above on the left to middle)

AJ Michalka.

First, I found that AJ starts to look a bit like Katy Mixon which was funny I didn’t find the resemblance before considering they both have been on a tv show on ABC network…

AJ has been on The Goldbergs

and Katy Mixon on

But I actually found she started to look somewhat different more like Reno Wilson (below in the middle) from Mike & Molly.

Ikr? How did I find the other half of resemblance?

Let’s rewind back to Mixon’s old show, Mike & Molly starting with some old castmates…

First, Reno from Mike & Molly then and now as good samaritan/cop now in Good Girls

and back then as Carl, Mike’s friend and business partner, Carl

Then, Molly below

including her sister played by Katy Mixon.

I found a bit of both of Katy & Reno in AJ Michalka and looking back, I found she really does start to look like a bit of the both of them.

How did I come to discover she starts to look like the two side-by-side? More about this below…

First, she starts to look like Katy Mixon having the same length of somewhat long, flat and trilateral, somewhat round shape.

Then, in width of shape I found that she starts to look like Reno Wilson having a much wider to almost more quadrilateral shaped like Reno’s.

In addition, she is well-known, has a talent for music on the Goldbergs show and way before, with her sister Aly.

You might of heard of Aly & AJ?

They now go by 78Violet that did a song for a few movies and shows

So basically then

and now,

I found that AJ Michalka starts to look a bit like both Katy Mixon and Reno Wilson.

Like the both known for her musical and comedic roles

and has almost lighter green to much darker blue-gray eyes, yet almost darker hazel to brown eyes,

natural brown hair and medium to dark hue of skin tone like the both.

Anyway, just when I start to think I see one more so, I see the other, 50/50.So who do you think she resembles more so?… I would love feedback on the poll. I would love to hear others’ perspective, feedback with the polls and/or comments.

More about the polls below…

Each one should have their own link and the poll can be available below. Clicking back should lead to main page.

I will be elaborating the combinations page. Thanks for visiting.
